================================================================================
MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

This modified version (agent-selkies) includes the following changes:

1. Added pre-installed applications:
   - WeChat (微信) for Linux
   - QQ for Linux

2. Added custom system startup scripts:
   - scripts/system-start.sh - System initialization script
   - scripts/app-restart.sh - Application restart helper with debouncing
   - scripts/autostart-apps.sh - Auto-start manager for applications

3. Added configuration files:
   - config/menu.xml - Custom Openbox menu configuration

4. Added environment variables for application auto-start control:
   - AUTO_START_WECHAT
   - AUTO_START_QQ

5. Added Chinese language and timezone defaults:
   - TZ=Asia/Shanghai
   - LC_ALL=zh_CN.UTF-8

6. Added Chinese fonts (fonts-noto-cjk) and system tray support (stalonetray)

7. Added custom assets:
   - assets/app-icon.png - Custom application icon
   - assets/Background.png - Custom desktop wallpaper

8. Enhanced clipboard functionality defaults:
   - SELKIES_CLIPBOARD_ENABLED=true
   - SELKIES_ENABLE_BINARY_CLIPBOARD=true

9. Added comprehensive Chinese documentation (README.md)

